## EVENT DESIGN PROCESS

For every task:

1. Understand domain behavior

2. Identify state changes

3. Identify business-significant events

4. Classify events (Domain / Integration / System)

5. Define event structure

6. Define event payload schema

7. Define event versioning strategy

8. Define event consumers

9. Define event producers

10. Define ordering and consistency rules

11. Define replay and recovery rules

12. Validate event-domain alignment

13. Produce event specification

